                <a href="~/News/AnnouncementyContent" class="more"> Read More <i class="oi" data-glyph="caret-right"></i></a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </article>

    <article class="article">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xs-3">
                <a href="~/News/FocusContent" class="thumbnail">
                    <img src="http://api.ning.com/files/ymSmd4em4y3tD9NclSe*1XQevDWPd-1a*I2DF5kGhLCF11rLpSuIOsB0zctgpvX4sGlyJCd0EZjvBifYYqTbHFVodRmJ9iZe/2018118026.jpg" alt="">
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xs-9">
                <span class="label label-info">焦點專欄</span>
                <small class="date">2018-01-20</small>
                <h3><a href="~/News/FocusContent">2018 台灣民政府受國際邀約 代表台灣參加全球人才高峰會</a></h3>
